ing out tonight.","a":"n_8f8b4a75d6ec.mp3"},{"t":"Darf ich eine Sache fragen?","en":"Can I ask one thing?","a":"n_969b259d3834.mp3"},{"t":"Wie sag ich dir das?","en":"How do I tell you this?","a":"n_2e1fc4af5475.mp3"},{"t":"Was sag ich ihm jetzt?","en":"What do I tell him now?","a":"n_78005f925426.mp3"},{"t":"Er kennt die Antwort.","en":"He knows the answer.","a":"n_cd08d25a7fec.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab ihr gedankt.","en":"I thanked her.","a":"n_023a95069dcb.mp3"},{"t":"Wir sind noch nicht bereit.","en":"We're not ready yet.","a":"n_6325b4608c2b.mp3"},{"t":"Ich brauch Zeit zum Nachdenken.","en":"I need time to think.","a":"n_730ec5645c1c.mp3"},{"t":"Mein Haus ist klein.","en":"My house is small.","a":"n_921140e551b9.mp3"},{"t":"Wir haben ein kleines Haus.","en":"We have a small house.","a":"n_cf96a9d47ea8.mp3"},{"t":"Ich mag dieses Lied.","en":"I like this song.","a":"n_e861b466cba9.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab nichts gesagt.","en":"I didn't say anything.","a":"n_65e514322227.mp3"},{"t":"Ich weiß schon, wie's geht.","en":"I already know how it works.","a":"n_f4dc6ab6031e.mp3"},{"t":"Sie steht früh auf.","en":"She gets up early.","a":"n_d8fa011caaaf.mp3"},{"t":"Was hast du zu trinken?","en":"What do you have to drink?","a":"n_dbe17be2e8d5.mp3"},{"t":"Kannst du mir mehr Brot bringen?","en":"Can you bring me more bread?","a":"n_ea573947e876.mp3"},{"t":"Sie wohnt zu Hause.","en":"She lives at home.","a":"n_40ebd139ea08.mp3"},{"t":"Ich arbeite bis sechs.","en":"I work until six.","a":"n_d7374a7506fe.mp3"},{"t":"Ich will mein Handy verkaufen.","en":"I want to sell my phone.","a":"n_89ef4cb886f8.mp3"},{"t":"Wo kauf ich die Karte?","en":"Where do I buy the ticket?","a":"n_f754ed6e7ce7.mp3"},{"t":"Mein Hals tut weh.","en":"My throat hurts.","a":"n_7a56d4b91fe4.mp3"},{"t":"Er ist ein Freund von mir.","en":"He's a friend of mine.","a":"n_2ceecd0a55e0.mp3"},{"t":"Die Freude ist ganz meinerseits.","en":"The pleasure is mine.","a":"n_900446da6289.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab heute echt viel zu tun.","e